{
  "stem": "6159.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in February, we were just shoveling the, the snow because we had to do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody for in front of their own house, there was no sanitary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my husband came rushing and said, put down the shovel because we're going to get married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] we went to the registration office, and of course, it was a, a quick, quick wedding because the people were queuing up for the weddings then.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was such a popular thing to do that everybody who found their relatives or, or beloved ones, they they all wanted to rejoice somehow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of marriages was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how my son's age group is a lot because a lot of my friends, and a lot of young girls got married in 1945, and the latest, '46.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And next year, they all have children, so we have now a generation of the same age group, practically, which is, you know, good, good for the children.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after when, when we were married, we went for a celebration at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tell you what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only had in the building-- in the house, I mean-- in the flat where we lived-- only those haricot beans, if you know what it is-- dried beans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister cooked something like a, a cholent, and that's what we had for celebration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the flat where we lived was shared with two other older women, and it was a two bedroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first night, we spent that time with my sister in the same room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was our wedding night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never forget that terrible, terrible times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the main thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, after that came also hard time with the communist and emigration-- not easy.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
